    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-black mb-1">Contact us</h1>
    <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color:rgb(var(--ink-rgb) / .55);margin:.15rem 0 1rem">We read every message and aim to reply within 24 hours.</p>

    <p>thaiholidaybudget.com is operated by <b>Genext Information Systems</b>. Whether you have found an out-of-date price or detail, have a question about the estimator, want to report a problem, or have a partnership or advertising enquiry, we would like to hear from you. Fill in the form below and we will get back to you.</p>

    <h2>Send us a message</h2>
    <p>Choose a topic and send us your message. We reply to the email address you provide, usually within 24 hours.</p>

    <form id="contactForm" name="contact" method="POST" action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" class="mt-3">
      <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="c394c121-5e53-49ec-be2b-3fdb67c9a3a3" />
      <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="New contact message — thaiholidaybudget.com" />
      <input type="hidden" name="from_name" value="ThaiHolidayBudget Contact Form" />
      <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" class="hidden" style="display:none;" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true" />

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-x-4">
        <div>
          <label class="lbl" for="c-name">Your name</label>
          <input id="c-name" name="name" class="field" type="text" placeholder="What should we call you?" autocomplete="name" required />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="lbl" for="c-email">Your email</label>
          <input id="c-email" name="email" class="field" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" autocomplete="email" required />
        </div>
      </div>

      <label class="lbl" for="c-topic">Topic</label>
      <select id="c-topic" name="topic" class="field">
        <option>General question</option>
        <option>Correction / out-of-date info</option>
        <option>Bug report</option>
        <option>Partnership / advertising enquiry</option>
        <option>Privacy request</option>
        <option>Something else</option>
      </select>

      <label class="lbl" for="c-msg">Message</label>
      <textarea id="c-msg" name="message" class="field" rows="5" placeholder="Tell us what's on your mind…" required></textarea>

      <button type="submit" class="btn-cta mt-4 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-xl">Send message →</button>
      <p id="formStatus" role="status" aria-live="polite" class="hidden text-sm font-semibold text-tealdeep pt-3">✓ Your message was sent — we'll reply by email. Thank you!</p>
      <p id="formError" role="alert" class="hidden text-sm font-semibold text-red-500 pt-3">Something went wrong sending your message. Please email us directly at support@thaiholidaybudget.com.</p>
    </form>

    <h2>What to include</h2>
    <p>To help us reply quickly and usefully, please include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><b>What it's about</b> — a correction, a question, a bug report, or a partnership/advertising enquiry.</li>
      <li><b>The detail</b> — if you are flagging an outdated price or detail, a link to the official source helps us verify and fix it fast.</li>
      <li><b>Where you saw it</b> — which page or which destination, if relevant.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="flex gap-3 items-start rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-5 my-6" style="background:rgba(20,184,166,.10);border:1px solid rgba(20,184,166,.25)">
      <span class="text-xl leading-none">ℹ️</span>
      <p class="m-0">We are an independent information site, <b>not</b> a travel agency, tour operator, or booking service. We can't make bookings, take payments, or arrange trips on your behalf — but we can help you get the most out of the estimator and point you to the right official sources.</p>
    </div>


    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>Anything you send us is used only to respond to your message. We don't add you to marketing lists or share your details. For privacy requests, choose <b>Privacy request</b> in the form above (these reach <a href="mailto:privacy@thaiholidaybudget.com">privacy@thaiholidaybudget.com</a>). See our <a href="privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a> for the full picture.</p>
  </div>


